snippet.title: Here Is Where I Carve My Heart, by Kitty Horrorshow
snippet.description:
I decided to record this and upload it on Youtube as I could not find any footage of this game/experience, and due to discontinued support of the Unity Web Player, I expect this to be harder and harder to experience as time marches on. 
I found this very much simple, but it still made me tear up. It's very nice.
